#. [display_tip]
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/utils/savescumming.cfg:116
msgid "Save-Loading and RNG"
msgstr "Tallennus-lataus ja satunnaisuus"

#. [display_tip]
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/utils/savescumming.cfg:118
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "I notice you’ve been loading a lot\n"
#| "of saved games. If this is how you prefer to play, \n"
#| "more power to you!\n"
#| "\n"
#| "But if you’re save-loading because hits and misses\n"
#| "feel unfair, try restarting the campaign and \n"
#| "selecting <i><b>“Reduced RNG”</b></i> instead of <i><b>“Default RNG”</b></"
#| "i>.\n"
#| "You’re also welcome to turn down the difficulty:\n"
#| "when you load a “start-of-scenario” save, there’s \n"
#| "a little <i><b>“change difficulty”</b></i> box you can check.\n"
#| "\n"
#| "Alternatively, you may want to go back to a previous\n"
#| "turn or even scenario, to choose a different strategy\n"
#| "or carry over additional gold.\n"
#| "\n"
#| "We balance campaigns around minimal save-loading \n"
#| "and have completed all campaigns without any \n"
#| "save-loading during development. It’s not expected to \n"
#| "beat campaigns without losses.\n"
#| "\n"
#| "Save-load all you want if it makes the game more fun,\n"
#| "but don’t feel like you’re required to save-load in \n"
#| "order to win!"
msgid ""
"I notice you’ve been loading a lot of saved games.\n"
"If this is how you prefer to play, power to you!\n"
"\n"
"But if you’re save-loading because hits and misses\n"
"feel unfair, try restarting the campaign and \n"
"selecting <i><b>“Reduced RNG”</b></i> instead of <i><b>“Default RNG”</b></"
"i>.\n"
"You’re also welcome to turn down the difficulty:\n"
"when you load a “start-of-scenario” save, there’s \n"
"a little <i><b>“change difficulty”</b></i> box you can check.\n"
"\n"
"Alternatively, you may want to go back to a previous\n"
"turn or even scenario, to choose a different strategy\n"
"or carry over additional gold.\n"
"\n"
"We balance campaigns around minimal save-loading \n"
"and have completed all campaigns without any \n"
"save-loading during development. It’s not expected to \n"
"beat campaigns without losses.\n"
"\n"
"Save-load all you want if it makes the game more fun,\n"
"but don’t feel like you’re required to save-load in \n"
"order to win!"
msgstr ""
"Näyt ladanneen paljon\n"
"pelitallennuksia. Jos niin haluat pelata,\n"
"voimia sinulle!\n"
"\n"
"Mutta jos tallennat ja lataat, koska osumat ja hudit\n"
"tuntuvat epäreiluilta, kokeile aloittaa kampanja uudelleen\n"
"ja valitse <i><b>“Vähennetty RNG”</b></i> <i><b>“Oletus-RNG:n”</b></i> "
"sijasta.\n"
"Voit myös kaikin mokomin alentaa vaikeusastetta:\n"
"kun lataat \"aloita-skenaario\"-tallenteen, voit\n"
"tarkistaa pientä <i><b>“vaihda vaikeusastetta”</b></i> -laatikkoa.\n"
"\n"
"Vaihtoehtoisesti voit halutessasi palata edelliseen vuoroon\n"
"tai jopa skenaarioon eri strategian valitsemiseksi\n"
"tai lisäkullan siirtämiseksi.\n"
"\n"
"Me tasapainotamme kampanjoita minimaalisella tallennus-latauksella,\n"
"ja olemme suorittaneet kaikki kampanjat tallentamatta ja\n"
"lataamatta kehityksen aikana. Kampanjoita ei\n"
"odoteta voitettavan ilman tappioita.\n"
"\n"
"Tallenna ja lataa mielin määrin, jos niin pelistä tulee hauskempi,\n"
"muttei pidä tuntea, että voittaakseen pitää\n"
"tallentaa ja lataa!"

