#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/utils/sg_characters.cfg:179
msgid ""
"They’ve broken through the trapdoor and entered the refugee cellar! Even if "
"we could still manage to win by force of arms, Westin is doomed without its "
"people..."
msgstr ""
"He ovat päässeet luukusta ja menneet turvakellariin! Vaikka me vielä "
"voittaisimmekin asevoimin, Westin on tuomittu ilman kansaansa..."

#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/utils/sg_characters.cfg:207
msgid "Taste cold steel!"
msgstr "Maista kylmää terästä!"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/utils/sg_characters.cfg:223
msgid "Yeah... I should’ve figured I wouldn’t get a happy ending..."
msgstr "Joo... Olisi pitänyt arvata, etten saisi onnellista loppua..."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/utils/sg_characters.cfg:242
msgid "I have given all in service of my kingdom..."
msgstr "Kaikkeni annoin kuningaskuntani puolesta..."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/utils/sg_characters.cfg:262
msgid "May the Light guide you where I have failed..."
msgstr "Ohjatkoon valo sinut sinne, missä olen epäonnistunut..."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/utils/sg_characters.cfg:282
msgid ""
"I have lost everything helping the humans... Now they will surely perish!"
msgstr "Menetin kaiken auttaessani ihmisiä... Nyt he ovat takuulla hukassa!"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/utils/sg_help.cfg:75
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "I have reached max XP, and advanced a level! I am now significantly more "
#| "powerful, and have been fully healed!\n"
#| "\n"
#| "For a full description of everything I can do, <b><i>right-click me and "
#| "select “Unit Description.”</i></b>"
msgid ""
"One of your units has reached max XP, and has advanced a level! It is now "
"significantly more powerful, and has been fully healed!\n"
"\n"
"For a full description of what one of your units can do, <b><i>right-click "
"it and select “Unit Type Description.”</i></b>"
msgstr ""
"Saavutin enimmäiskokemuksen ja nousin tasossa! Olen nyt huomattavasti "
"vahvempi ja täysin parantunut!\n"
"\n"
"Täyden kuvauksen kaikesta osaamisestani saat <b><i>napsauttamalla minua "
"hiiren oikealla ja valitsemalla “Yksikön kuvaus”.</i></b>"

#. [display_tip]
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/utils/sg_help.cfg:94
msgid ""
"\n"
"Most scenarios have a turn limit, as\n"
"shown in the upper-left-hand corner.\n"
"Usually, running out of turns will\n"
"result in defeat — check your\n"
"<i><b>objectives</b></i> by clicking the <i><b>“Menu”</b></i>\n"
"button in the top-left corner \n"
"(or use the hotkey <i><b>Ctrl+J</b></i>).\n"
"\n"
"Finishing early will usually reward \n"
"a gold boost (“early finish bonus”) \n"
"in the next scenario, so don’t delay!"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Useimmissa skenaarioissa on vuororaja,\n"
"kuten vasemmassa yläkulmassa näkyy.\n"
"Vuorojen loppuminen johtaa yleensä\n"
"tappioon — tarkasta\n"
"<i><b>tavoitteet</b></i> napsauttamalla <i><b>“Valikko”</b></i>\n"
"-nappia vasemmassa yläkulmassa\n"
"(tai pikanapilla <i><b>Ctrl+J</b></i>).\n"
"\n"
"Aikainen lopetus palkitsee yleensä \n"
"lisäkullalla (“aikaisen lopetuksen bonus”) \n"
"seuraavassa skenaariossa, joten älä kuhni!"

#. [message]: id=Ethiliel,Hylas {NOT race=mechanical}
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/utils/sg_help.cfg:129
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "My healing magic is potent, but I cannot use it to heal myself. I’ll have "
#| "to end my turn on a village to recover."
msgid ""
"My healing magic is potent, but I cannot use it to heal myself. I’ll have to "
"spend some time in a village to recover."
msgstr ""
"Parannustaikani on vahvaa, mutta en voi käyttää sitä itseeni. Minun on "
"päätettävä vuoroni kylässä toipuakseni."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/utils/sg_help.cfg:151
